description: AMUNDI JPX-NIKKEI 400 UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED USD (C) seeks to replicate as closely as possible the evolution of the performance of the yen-denominated JPX-Nikkei 400 index (net dividends reinvested), whether the trend is rising of falling and has a monthly currency hedging in USD. This ETF enables investors to benefit from an exposure to a selection of Japanese stocks selected according to quantitative criteria and qualitative criteria relating to corporate governance, and weighted according to their market capitalization. For further information, please also refer to the fund prospectus.
name: Amundi JPX-Nikkei 400 UCITS ETF - DAILY HEDGED USD (C)
